    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sketchy Marathon is an arcade platformer following the journey of a stick figure trying to escape its creator. Explore the world of Sketchy Marathon and survive its many dangers as you make your way towards the next milestone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235640/extras/d67fbd56f8d260c50be0e82ec59c4174.avif?t=1728952851\" width=550 height=550 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different biomes, each with their own dangers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a variety of challenge events, that force you to adapt to unique scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges and be rewarded with portals that boost your progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hearts to take a hit for you, because if you die, you're back to square one</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach new milestones to unlock new looks for your character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track your progress as you make your way through the world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the final milestone to finally achieve happiness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235640/extras/0f10afac2b32043bb08d1720e24be8ce.avif?t=1728952851\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p>",
